{"tid":824663,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"三星 Note 9 爆咗啦～ 過熱出煙，用戶起訴要求禁售","createTime":"2018-09-17T07:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T02:16:37.000Z","uid":23677,"like":53,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"0ab2c089e15a4b765580bc892e1d86874cbcb6bc","tid":824663,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:22:40.000Z","msg":"對於 Galaxy Note 7 的全球連環爆炸事件，引起全球航空禁攜機上飛機，最後全球回收，成為全球「最短命手機」，估計大家可能仍然心有餘悸。今年來到 Note 9，不幸的事又再發生，全球首宗 Note 9 意外在開賣後不足一個月就已經發生。<br />\n<br />\n在紐約的 Diane Chung 當時正在皇后區 Bayside 公寓乘搭升降機，她發現手機有點熱，於是停止使用並放入手袋，之後手機開始發出刺耳的聲音並開始釋出濃煙。於是她快速拿出手機，並放到地上。Diane Chung表示當時極度恐慌，升降機內只有其一人，她立即按下升降機按鈕令，門打開後正好在公寓大堂，於是她快速把地上的手機踢出門口，一名路人幫忙用水澆熄手機。<br />\n<br />\n事件之後 Diane Chung 通過律師向 Samsung 提出訴訟，她認為 Samsung 應知 Note 9 有缺憾，要求 Samsung 賠償損失及提出銷售禁令。Samsung 回應「未收到涉及 Galaxy Note9 的類似事件的任何報告，我們正在調查此事。」<br />\n<br />\nSamsung 爆炸小檔案：<br />\n在 Galaxy Note 7 爆炸事件發生初期，Samsung 一直對外否認自身產品設計有問題，甚至有地區服務點認為是用戶自家使用不當引致，最後爆炸事件完全不能停止。Samsung 在輿論壓力下終全球回收。半年之後，Samsung 發表調查報告，終承認自身電池設計在製造過程中產生問題。全球回收超過250萬部。<br />\n<br />\nGalaxy Note 7 當時使用 3500mAh電池，而到了 Galaxy Note 8 Samsung 改用低一點的 3300mAh 電池，不過 Galaxy Note 9 卻是全系列最大電池 4000mAh。估計如果爆起來威力亦是歷來最強。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2018/09/17/galaxy-note-9-explosion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2Fgalaxy-note-9-explosion%2F&d=ZeZ6tPDxC3becklY%2FXKFRBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d4e64cfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2018/09/17/galaxy-note-9-explosion/</a>"},{"pid":"d3e79b37a813b5c931bffb38d0ef002eb7c8f45c","tid":824663,"uid":109383,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:25:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">召<br />\n喚<br />\n火<br />\n星<br />\n達<br />\n人</span></span>"},{"pid":"5529185b6d787a78e62e3d9a84fce51905f6e9b8","tid":824663,"uid":6556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"會爆炸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會爆炸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一路爆炸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d594ef472892e9ef14ddadcb4564acc4f6a08c92","tid":824663,"uid":164092,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:26:27.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"1970f88e31796966c8445a754309878e0ed688d0","tid":824663,"uid":151956,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:27:50.000Z","msg":"肯撚定喺用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（三星打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"992ad8701c3386ef02be8db0719503209f860f34","tid":824663,"uid":141060,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係爆就好 可以免費換gay"},{"pid":"1cabc78f67eca90513b2aa61b50c9f71c03f9889","tid":824663,"uid":109383,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"992ad8701c3386ef02be8db0719503209f860f34","tid":824663,"uid":141060,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係爆就好 可以免費換gay"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:31:37.000Z","msg":"全球回收 唔包括香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e3292d9dfc9e2d3e68946be046ba2abb515e8f","tid":824663,"uid":34213,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:32:48.000Z","msg":"用qc2.0都著得火"},{"pid":"0ba6c3ec14adf54c42728367b1ce862a51ed68aa","tid":824663,"uid":99700,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"1cabc78f67eca90513b2aa61b50c9f71c03f9889","tid":824663,"uid":109383,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"992ad8701c3386ef02be8db0719503209f860f34","tid":824663,"uid":141060,"like":2,"dislike":4,"scor